Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情提要\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你想不想嫁给我\N{\fs12}I don't care if you don't want to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我做好当爸爸的准备了\N{\fs12}I know that I'm ready to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那么多的家长  都会让孩子失望\N{\fs12}So many parents fail their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我不是同性恋\N{\fs12}Look, I'm not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,匹兹堡是个小地方\N{\fs12}Pittsburgh is a small town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,议论我\N{\fs12}Talking about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺你完成了戒断程序\N{\fs12}Congratulations for completing your program.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我们的事儿\N{\fs12}About us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你能就试着  - 试一试吗\N{\fs12}- if you could try to just... - Try?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对  试一试\N{\fs12}Right... try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨  外面真冷啊\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hi. It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在很晚了  你还好吗\N{\fs12}It's, um-- It's late. You-- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不好  我  我睡不着\N{\fs12}I'm sorry. No, l, uh-- I just couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要来杯茶\N{\fs12}Um, you want some tea or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子出了点问题\N{\fs12}There's a problem with the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么问题\N{\fs12}What kind of problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,唐氏综合症\N{\fs12}Down syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,三倍显示检查的时候\N{\fs12}I got the results of my triple marker screening,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,显示这个孩子可能有\N{\fs12}and, uh, it indicated that there could be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,得唐氏综合症的可能\N{\fs12}some kind of a problem like this with the baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以为了搞清楚情况  我做了羊水检测  今天结果出来了\N{\fs12}so I had to go ahead and get an amnio, and I got those results today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,之前为什么不告诉我\N{\fs12}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在不确定之前  我不想因为\N{\fs12}Because I just didn't want to bother you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情打扰你\N{\fs12}with something like this until I knew for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧  现在确定了吗\N{\fs12}Right. Right. Well, is it for certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,羊水测试有百分之九十九的可能\N{\fs12}Amnio. It's 99%.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  医生\N{\fs12}Um, the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给了我这个\N{\fs12}gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道这个到底有没有用\N{\fs12}I mean, I don't know how much it's really gonna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在都不知道我要什么了\N{\fs12}I don't-- I don't even know what I really want right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我不知道我们能不能接受拥有一个这样的小孩\N{\fs12}I mean, I don't know that we can handle having a child like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fs12}''We''?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了  明天再说吧\N{\fs12}I'm gonna go. Let's talk about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以当时在吃晚饭\N{\fs12}So, we sit down to dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,门铃响了\N{\fs12}and the doorbell rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有在意\N{\fs12}I ignore it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是门铃一直响  有人在一直敲门\N{\fs12}but it keeps ringing, and somebody keeps knocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我去开门了  结果是两个警察\N{\fs12}So I go to answer it, and these two cops come into my house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,和两个社会服务的女人来了\N{\fs12}with two women from Social Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂尔登先生  等我一下\N{\fs12}Mr. Tilden, can you just give me one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会儿就来\N{\fs12}One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我确实犯了一个错\N{\fs12}You know, just 'cause I've made mistakes--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道我犯错了  但是露露\N{\fs12}Now, I know that I've made mistakes, but, Lulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不管遇到什么问题我们都能一起解决\N{\fs12}I think that we can work out whatever problems we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以千万不要因为我们现在的关系影响了你的决定\N{\fs12}So just don't let us interfere with this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的已经过去了  尼克\N{\fs12}Well, the past is prologue, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已经发生的我也不能当它没发生\N{\fs12}You know, all I have to go on is what's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很感谢你对我说这样的话\N{\fs12}So you can say these things. It's nice. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是这改变不了任何事 - 我说什么都没用了吗\N{\fs12}- But it doesn't really change anything. - Does what I say have any bearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这跟我一点关系都没有吗  - 当然有\N{\fs12}- Am I not involved in this? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,医生有没有跟你说我们还有多长时间\N{\fs12}The doctor tell you how much time we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我已经处于孕中期了  - 但是我们还有时间吗\N{\fs12}- I'm in my second trimester, so-- - But do we have any time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了\N{\fs12}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  我已经等了一早上了\N{\fs12}Hey, I've been waiting all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回去\N{\fs12}I gotta get back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs12}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要谈谈的话\N{\fs12}lf you need to talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  我没事\N{\fs12}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子有唐氏综合症\N{\fs12}The baby has Down syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你来读一读这篇文章\N{\fs12}And you, uh-- you read this material,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,上面就是些没用的话  你知道吗\N{\fs12}and it's all just words, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,多一条染色体  心脏缺陷  发育迟缓\N{\fs12}Just extra chromosome, heart defects, retardation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只是些介绍罢了\N{\fs12}It's just all words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要我的话\N{\fs12}lf there's anything I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂尔登先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Tilden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,社会服务说他们接到了一个电话\N{\fs12}So, Social Services said they got a call
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有人举报我  说我性侵了我自己的女儿梅根\N{\fs12}that someone had accused me of molesting my daughter, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我要在我家查一查\N{\fs12}and they told me I had to let them look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接着警察就让我坐在角落里的沙发上\N{\fs12}Next thing I know, the cops have me on the couch in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带走了我的女儿们\N{\fs12}and they took the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有三个女儿啊  - 嗯  梅根  辛迪和艾米\N{\fs12}- You have three girls? - Megan, Cindy, and Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她们现在在哪里  - 在她们的爷爷奶奶家\N{\fs12}- Where are they now? - At their grandparents'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爸妈家吗  - 我岳父岳母那儿\N{\fs12}- Your parents? - My wife's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你太太呢  - 在县医院\N{\fs12}- Where's your wife? - At the county hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她什么时候能出院  - 不\N{\fs12}- When does she get out? - She doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经昏迷了好几年了\N{\fs12}She's been in a coma for four years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她出不了院\N{\fs12}so she doesn't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天下午在法庭见  住所听证会三点开始\N{\fs12}So, I'll meet you outside the courthouse at 3:OO for the shelter hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,残疾人之家\N{\fs12}The Home for the Developmentally Disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经代理他们超过十年了\N{\fs12}We've been representing their residents for over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有个23岁的患有唐氏综合症的孩子\N{\fs12}So, there's this 23-year-old kid with Down syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是要帮他解决遗嘱的问题的\N{\fs12}I'm supposed to help him deal with a probate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  - 如果你想要的话  这个案子就交给你了\N{\fs12}- Okay. - If you want, you can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给我\N{\fs12}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过  这不过是书面的话罢了  对吗\N{\fs12}You said it was all just words, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是遗嘱的事情吗\N{\fs12}It's a probate issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  很高兴大家今天能赏脸过来\N{\fs12}Gentlemen, it's good to have you with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  正如你们所知  里弗布鲁克乡村俱乐部\N{\fs12}Now, as you may know, the Riverbrook Country Club
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是匹兹堡最古老最有声望的俱乐部之一\N{\fs12}is one of Pittsburgh's oldest and most prestigious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的会员涵盖了商务精英  政治领袖以及知名慈善家\N{\fs12}Our members include leaders in business, politics, and philanthropy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,每一年我们都期待会见\N{\fs12}Every year, we look forward to meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一些正式会员候选人\N{\fs12}a select number ofjunior member candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经从你们的赞助商那边听到了很多关于你们的好消息\N{\fs12}We've heard good things about all of you from your sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们期待在你们申请会员的过程中能\N{\fs12}So now we look forward to getting to know you better
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,更加深入地了解你们\N{\fs12}during your application process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请随我前往花园\N{\fs12}Follow me out to the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs12}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,凯特  嗨\N{\fs12}Kate. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你来这儿干嘛  - 我只是来参观的\N{\fs12}- What are you doing here? - Oh, uh, just orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你懂的  我想融入  - 好极了\N{\fs12}- You know, I was trying to join. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以喜欢高尔夫和网球\N{\fs12}Yeah, you know, maybe-- I like golf and tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你是会员吗\N{\fs12}So, are you, uh-- are you a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的高曾祖父之前帮忙建立了这地方  所以\N{\fs12}Oh, my great-great-grandfather helped found the place, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Really?
