Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.38,0:40:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想想但是这  这一切都被愈合了\N{\fs12}think but this-- this all is mended.''
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.89,0:40:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你去了\N{\fs12}Glad you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.75,0:40:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我也很开心我去了\N{\fs12}Yeah. I'm glad that I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.96,0:40:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他表现得很好\N{\fs12}He did really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  基本上那个角色就是他了\N{\fs12}Yeah, well, he's quite the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.66,0:40:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.74,0:40:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚给你写了张纸条\N{\fs12}I was just writing you a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.20,0:40:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是孩子欢迎会的礼物\N{\fs12}These are the presents from the baby shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.92,0:40:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦  我忘了你要来了  不好意思\N{\fs12}Yeah, I forgot you were coming. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.94,0:40:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你\N{\fs12}Right. Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.51,0:40:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.35,0:40:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见了\N{\fs12}Well, I'll see you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.00,0:40:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  我再打给你  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Yeah. I'll call you. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.52,0:40:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.70,0:41:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.81,0:41:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.12,0:41:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么了\N{\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.82,0:41:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们不应该把这些礼物送回去\N{\fs12}Well, maybe we shouldn't send them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.89,0:41:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.57,0:41:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fs12}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.42,0:41:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.91,0:41:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I have no idea.
